{"id": 1484, "genre": 1001, "title": "这年头，你觉得你爸妈的网瘾主要都体现在什么地方？", "description": "为什么现在你打游戏他们不管了？因为他们自己更加沉迷网络啊。（题图来自：Kathryn Macnaughton）", "record_count": 4529, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170207124019Omgsvu9A6wtNyLq2.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-08T03:00:20Z", "options": [{"id": 164608, "content": "玩微信斗地主看新闻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922963}, {"id": 163841, "content": "中午不回来吃饭 这一句话都要开视屏讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929637}, {"id": 168961, "content": "螺丝钉也要在某宝买...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941617}, {"id": 164098, "content": "爸妈只玩手机，彼此都不讲话了，大年夜也就我一个人在看春晚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779220}, {"id": 168450, "content": "疯狂看韩剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061245}, {"id": 164099, "content": "看片打游戏美图秀秀写诗歌群组聊天网购 我关了在自己房间的路由器 她半夜会偷偷进来开?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922763}, {"id": 169219, "content": "斗地主", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942131}, {"id": 163845, "content": "看小说?", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929060}, {"id": 165125, "content": "又发红包快抢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810467}, {"id": 165381, "content": "打开电视玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928591}, {"id": 163846, "content": "抢红包，看新闻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925650}, {"id": 164102, "content": "消消乐款游戏让退休后的他们重获成就感，故此一发不可收拾。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930262}, {"id": 164103, "content": "我老爸是部落战的深度玩家…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147283}, {"id": 163848, "content": "手机麻将，斗地主", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581023}, {"id": 164104, "content": "同学群", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708088}, {"id": 165384, "content": "打开电视玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928591}, {"id": 292873, "content": "老妈刷抖音", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1400424}, {"id": 163593, "content": "跟朋友聊天比我还嗨?", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922117}, {"id": 163849, "content": "随时在线", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929663}, {"id": 164105, "content": "以前早睡的父母现在会躺床上看小说玩游戏到很晚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280233}, {"id": 168457, "content": "他们和我们刚接触网络的状态都一样，相互理解。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402772}, {"id": 163850, "content": "家里农村、没有手机、只有电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734510}, {"id": 164106, "content": "过年的时候专注的抢红包", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930274}, {"id": 164362, "content": "追剧根本停不下来，视频电话总是突如其来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883179}, {"id": 167690, "content": "写的都太有意思了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938916}, {"id": 163851, "content": "微信‘不可不看’的养生文", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892939}, {"id": 164107, "content": "抢红包，炒菜都让我给她盯着，玩欢乐麻将～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865851}, {"id": 164619, "content": "沉迷拍照", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926851}, {"id": 163596, "content": "凡事问百度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535986}, {"id": 163597, "content": "自从教了她天天P图，动不动上传把自己变成各种精灵，各种动漫人物的照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928349}, {"id": 163853, "content": "反正我一放学回家就看到我爸在看各种科幻剧。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929445}, {"id": 164109, "content": "抢红包，各种小视频。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705988}, {"id": 164621, "content": "开心消消乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931176}, {"id": 163598, "content": "高频次转发标题惊悚的各类消息", "image": null, "praise_count": 828, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776013}, {"id": 163854, "content": "抱着平板沉迷于各种消消乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739074}, {"id": 164110, "content": "抢微信红包……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 501445}, {"id": 165902, "content": "天天在淘宝上买衣服然后在微信上晒自拍 用生命在买衣服￼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796731}, {"id": 163599, "content": "家庭群里全是他们的聊天记录", "image": null, "praise_count": 153, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926317}, {"id": 164623, "content": "天天爱消除?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931174}, {"id": 163600, "content": "玩全民小镇一玩玩一天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910158}, {"id": 163856, "content": "打腾讯五子棋。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927576}, {"id": 164112, "content": "用微信召集大妈来打麻将，实在不够人就自个儿玩麻将app", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797034}, {"id": 165392, "content": "鸡汤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926063}, {"id": 166672, "content": "他们看字费劲 所以各种小视频", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936791}, {"id": 163601, "content": "斗地主…", "image": null, "praise_count": 207, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690822}, {"id": 164113, "content": "沉迷各种消消乐。追各种剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 